<item>
            <title>[HIVE-4820] webhcat_config.sh should set default values for HIVE_HOME and HCAT_PREFIX that work with default build tree structure</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-4820</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently they are expected to be set by the user which makes development inconvenient.&lt;br/&gt;
It makes writing unit tests for WebHcat more difficult as well.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12656654">HIVE-4820</key>
            <summary>webhcat_config.sh should set default values for HIVE_HOME and HCAT_PREFIX that work with default build tree structure</summary>
